<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='632000' id='t-632000'>Forms of organization can have a profound impact on human nature.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='637000' id='t-637000'>Looking ahead, there is a range of technologies</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='639000' id='t-639000'>that are almost certain to be developed sooner or later.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='642000' id='t-642000'>We are very ignorant about what the time scale for these things are,</span>
