<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='715000' id='t-715000'>and to remember what you have learned.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='719000' id='t-719000'>Modalities and special faculties.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='721000' id='t-721000'>Now, the human mind is not a single unitary information processor,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='726000' id='t-726000'>but it has a lot of different, special, evolved modules</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='730000' id='t-730000'>that do specific things for us.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='732000' id='t-732000'>If you think about what we normally take as giving life a lot of its meaning --</span>
