<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='740000' id='t-740000'>nurturing and caring, gossip, chatting with people --</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:36
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='745000' id='t-745000'>all of these, very likely, are enabled by a special circuitry</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='749000' id='t-749000'>that we humans have,</span>
