<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='781000' id='t-781000'>with other values that there might be?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:14
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='783000' id='t-783000'>Imagine a species</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='785000' id='t-785000'>that just didn't have this neural machinery for processing music.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='789000' id='t-789000'>And they would just stare at us with bafflement</span>
