<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='892000' id='t-892000'>A possible mode of being here would be a way of life --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='895000' id='t-895000'>a way of being, experiencing, thinking, seeing,</span>
