<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='913000' id='t-913000'>It's a part of the space that's accessible to animals;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='916000' id='t-916000'>since we are animals, we are a subset of that.</span>
</span>
